subject: Soccer
Gold Cup (Soccer)
organizations: Confederation of North, Central American and Caribbean Association Football (CONCACAF)
lead_paragraph: Dempsey, who last week relinquished the U.S. captaincy to Michael Bradley, scored twice as the Americans held on for a 2-1 win.
